t;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31940,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/10\/zakat-al-fitr-purification\/","url_meta":{"origin":3721,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Zakat al-Fitr as purification for misbehavior","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 10, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, obligated Zakat al-Fitr as purification of the fasting person from vain talk and misbehavior, as food for the poor. Whoever pays it before the Eid prayer, it is accepted as Zakat. Whoever pays it after the Eid\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31842,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/08\/waki-zakat-al-fitr-sujud-sahw\/","url_meta":{"origin":3721,"position":2},"title":"Waki\u2019 on Ramadan: Zakat al-Fitr like prostration of forgetfulness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Nawawi reported: Waki\u2019 ibn al-Jarrah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cZakat al-Fitr is to the month of Ramadan like the prostration of forgetfulness is to prayer. It makes up for deficiencies in fasting just as the prostration makes up for deficiencies in prayer.\u201d Source: al-Majmu\u0304\u2019 Sharh\u0323 al-Muhadhab 6\/140\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5037,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/12\/prophet-dates-eid-al-fitr\/","url_meta":{"origin":3721,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Eid: The Prophet eats dates before Eid prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would not proceed on the day of Eid al-Fitr\u00a0until he had eaten some dates. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 953 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33845,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/12\/22\/ayat-al-kursi-protection-shaytan\/","url_meta":{"origin":3721,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ayat al-Kursi: Verse of Throne for protection from Satan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 22, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, entrusted me to protect the charity of Ramadan. Someone came to me and began taking from the food. I took hold of him, and I said, \u201cI will certainly take you to the Messenger of Allah!\u201d Abu\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4035,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/03\/fasting-haram-eid-fitr-adha-tashriq\/","url_meta":{"origin":3721,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Eid: The Prophet forbids fasting on the two Eids","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu 'Ubayd reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cO people, the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, has prohibited you from fasting on the days of these two celebrations, Eid al-Fitr and Eid al-Adha. One of them is the day you break\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3721","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3721"}],"version-history":[{"count"